(uint8_t *dst, uint8_t *src, int width)

{

#ifdef HAVE_MMX

	asm volatile(

		"movq "MANGLE(bm01010101)", %%mm2\n\t"

		"mov %0, %%"REG_a"		\n\t"

		"1:				\n\t"

		"movq (%1, %%"REG_a",2), %%mm0	\n\t"

		"movq 8(%1, %%"REG_a",2), %%mm1	\n\t"

		"pand %%mm2, %%mm0		\n\t"

		"pand %%mm2, %%mm1		\n\t"

		"packuswb %%mm1, %%mm0		\n\t"

		"movq %%mm0, (%2, %%"REG_a")	\n\t"

		"add $8, %%"REG_a"		\n\t"

		" js 1b				\n\t"

		: : "g" ((long)-width), "r" (src+width*2), "r" (dst+width)

		: "%"REG_a

	);

#else

	int i;

	for(i=0; i<width; i++)

		dst[i]= src[2*i];

#endif

}
